PrecisEnactment of THE JACQUES-CARTIER AND CHAMPLAIN BRIDGES INC. REGULATIONS which provide that subsection 3(2) and sections 4, 9, 16, 17, 22, 24 and 25 of the St. Lawrence Seaway Authority Act, as it read on November 30, 1998, shall apply, in a modified form, to these bridge companies, effective December 1, 1998.
